#: templates/webhooks-tab.php:34
msgid "\"Last Attempt\" instead shows the most recent time this webhook fired for real — e.g. when you actually published a post — and which event triggered it. It won't always show a pass/fail mark, because real triggers fire in the background without waiting to hear back; use \"Send Test\" if you want a definite yes/no."
msgstr ""

#: templates/webhooks-tab.php:31
msgid "\"Send Test\" fires a one-off trial call right now, using sample data, and tells you immediately whether it succeeded or failed (with the reason). Use it after saving a webhook to confirm it's set up correctly."
msgstr ""

